cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper deals with logo detection using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of data expansion through synthesising context also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The paper also uses image retrieval (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques for benchmarking and evaluating the proposed method.
